Character-Aware Convolutional Neural Network for Paraphrase Identification
==========================================================================


## Information:
- Author: Jiangping Huang.
- Date: Wed, 14 Dec, 2016.
- E-Mail: hjp@whu.edu.cn.


## Description:
Code to train convolutional neural network paraphrase detection models as 
described in our ICONIP 2016 paper.


## Features:
- Character-level input for convolutional neural networks.
- Dynamic k-max pooling operation on feature map matrices.
- Variable sentence sequence to fixed-length feature vector.
- Both CPU and GPU enabled for implemented this code.
- Both narrow and wide convolution operations are considered.


## Citations:
If you make use of this code in your research, please cite our paper:
